		SILVERS are worth 5 points.<br />
		Each vote is worth 1 point.<br /><br />

		We may change the calculation for Painterscore in the future.<br />
		If you've got an oppinion on how many points to give to GOLDS and SILVERS <%= link_to	"let us know", contact_path %>.
		</div>
		
			<br /><br />
